title: Catit Chicken Dinner Duck & Potato
descriptions: Catit Dinner is a dual-layered wet food, made of fresh ingredients served in luscious gravy. This premium-quality cat food is natural, high in protein and grain-free, with added vitamins and minerals for precisely balanced nutrition. As wholesome as it was home-cooked, Catit Chicken Dinner has been carefully balanced as to create the ideal, hydrating complement to your cat’s daily dry food intake. It provides them with everything they need to keep happy and healthy.
key_benefits: As cat owners, we all want the best for our felines. Catit Chicken Dinner is high in protein and made with the best, non-GMO ingredients. It does not contain low-quality fillers like corn, wheat or soy, that are harder for cats to digest and metabolize. No artificial flavors or colors are used either. The seafood ingredients are dolphin-safe. On top of these fresh ingredients, we add zinc, iron, copper, manganese and vitamins A, B1, B3, B6, B7, B12 and E. Furthermore, Catit Chicken Dinner contains taurine, an essential nutrient that helps your cat maintain a normal digestion, heart muscle function, eyesight and a healthy immune system.
ingredients: Vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, Thiamine Hydrochloride, Niacin, Vitamin A Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Biotin, Vitamin B12 Supplement)
